{"article_id":"5xEIFhH1eEofLLrz","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Story highlights","depth":1},{"id":1,"text":"Co-author of expanded background checks proposal to meet with senators next week","depth":9},{"id":2,"text":"Sen. Joe Manchin , D-West Virginia , is seeing","depth":10},{"id":3,"text":"if he can change legislation","depth":11},{"id":4,"text":"to get more votes","depth":11},{"id":5,"text":"Gun-control activists have hounded some senators over their vote against the measure","depth":8},{"id":6,"text":"Behind-the-scenes dealing over reviving stalled gun control legislation will get a push next week","depth":10},{"id":7,"text":"when Sen. Joe Manchin , a strong proponent of expanding background checks , plans to meet individually with lawmakers ,","depth":10},{"id":8,"text":"a Senate source tells CNN .","depth":9},{"id":9,"text":"The key question","depth":11},{"id":10,"text":"the conservative West Virginia Democrat wants answered","depth":11},{"id":11,"text":"is whether a `` minimal change '' to a compromise background check proposal","depth":12},{"id":12,"text":"that he co-authored","depth":13},{"id":13,"text":"but which failed to gain enough support in a vote last month","depth":13},{"id":14,"text":"would entice more senators to support it ,","depth":11},{"id":15,"text":"the source said .","depth":9},{"id":16,"text":"Since the proposal","depth":11},{"id":17,"text":"he negotiated with Republican Sen. Pat Toomey of Pennsylvania","depth":11},{"id":18,"text":"faltered ,","depth":10},{"id":19,"text":"senators","depth":11},{"id":20,"text":"who voted against it","depth":11},{"id":21,"text":"have been hounded in their states during the current recess by outside proponents of expanding background checks .","depth":10},{"id":22,"text":"Sen. Kelly Ayotte has been the most high-profile target of such confrontations .","depth":9},{"id":23,"text":"The New Hampshire Republican was questioned at an event by Erica Lafferty , the daughter of Dawn Hochsprung , a school principal","depth":11},{"id":24,"text":"slain in the Newtown massacre last December .","depth":11},{"id":25,"text":"Lafferty asked","depth":11},{"id":26,"text":"`` why the burden of my mother","depth":14},{"id":27,"text":"being gunned down in the halls of her elementary school","depth":14},{"id":28,"text":"is n't as important ''","depth":13},{"id":29,"text":"as inconveniencing gun sellers .","depth":12},{"id":30,"text":"JUST WATCHED Giffords battles for NRA member votes","depth":11},{"id":31,"text":"Replay More Videos ...","depth":11},{"id":32,"text":"MUST WATCH Giffords battles for NRA member votes","depth":11},{"id":33,"text":"03:03","depth":11},{"id":34,"text":"JUST WATCHED","depth":13},{"id":35,"text":"Newtown victim 's daughter faces Ayotte","depth":13},{"id":36,"text":"Replay More Videos ...","depth":12},{"id":37,"text":"MUST WATCH","depth":13},{"id":38,"text":"Newtown victim 's daughter faces Ayotte","depth":13},{"id":39,"text":"03:42","depth":12},{"id":40,"text":"JUST WATCHED","depth":13},{"id":41,"text":"Gun vote follows senators home","depth":14},{"id":42,"text":"Replay More Videos ...","depth":14},{"id":43,"text":"MUST WATCH Gun vote follows senators home","depth":12},{"id":44,"text":"03:49","depth":13},{"id":45,"text":"JUST WATCHED","depth":14},{"id":46,"text":"Newtown victim 's daughter not giving up","depth":14},{"id":47,"text":"Replay More Videos ...","depth":13},{"id":48,"text":"MUST WATCH","depth":15},{"id":49,"text":"Newtown victim 's daughter not giving up","depth":15},{"id":50,"text":"04:29","depth":14},{"id":51,"text":"Lafferty was sent to Ayotte 's event by Mayors Against Illegal Guns , one of several gun control groups","depth":10},{"id":52,"text":"using the current congressional recess","depth":11},{"id":53,"text":"to take the gun control message out of Washington .","depth":11},{"id":54,"text":"And she followed that up with interviews with TV networks .","depth":9},{"id":55,"text":"The source said","depth":8},{"id":56,"text":"this sort of pressure from outside groups is a key to any hopes","depth":9},{"id":57,"text":"of swaying senators","depth":10},{"id":58,"text":"who may be open to supporting a modified proposal .","depth":10},{"id":59,"text":"In addition to confronting senators in person ,","depth":10},{"id":60,"text":"groups have run ads against lawmakers","depth":12},{"id":61,"text":"who voted against the Toomey-Manchin compromise","depth":12},{"id":62,"text":"and have supported senators","depth":12},{"id":63,"text":"who supported it .","depth":12},{"id":64,"text":"The husband of former Rep. Gabrielle Giffords ,","depth":12},{"id":65,"text":"who was seriously wounded in a 2011 shooting in Arizona ,","depth":12},{"id":66,"text":"wrote an opinion piece in the Houston Chronicle","depth":12},{"id":67,"text":"challenging the National Rifle Association over its opposition to expanded background checks .","depth":12},{"id":68,"text":"`` What most members of the NRA want from the organization and what the leadership is actually doing are not the same , ''","depth":11},{"id":69,"text":"Mark Kelly wrote .","depth":11},{"id":70,"text":"Thousands of NRA members are gathered in Houston this weekend for its annual convention .","depth":8},{"id":71,"text":"According to the Senate source ,","depth":8},{"id":72,"text":"the pressure tactics appear to be working","depth":9},{"id":73,"text":"with polls","depth":10},{"id":74,"text":"showing","depth":11},{"id":75,"text":"most Americans","depth":12},{"id":76,"text":"favoring some sort of new gun restrictions .","depth":12},{"id":77,"text":"The signal","depth":13},{"id":78,"text":"Manchin has been getting","depth":13},{"id":79,"text":"from senators","depth":13},{"id":80,"text":"getting hammered at home ,","depth":13},{"id":81,"text":"according to the source ,","depth":11},{"id":82,"text":"is that they need to save face politically","depth":10},{"id":83,"text":"and any deal would hinge on whether they can argue","depth":10},{"id":84,"text":"that they extracted something new in the language .","depth":10},{"id":85,"text":"`` We have to figure out some sort of new sentence , one change to it","depth":11},{"id":86,"text":"so they can go back and say","depth":12},{"id":87,"text":"' I fought to change this , ' ''","depth":12},{"id":88,"text":"said the source .","depth":10},{"id":89,"text":"At this point , however , it is not clear what the change would be .","depth":9},{"id":90,"text":"In order to pass any legislation around the issue ,","depth":7},{"id":91,"text":"gun control advocates need find 60 votes in the Senate .","depth":7},{"id":92,"text":"Fifty-four senators backed the Mancin-Toomey amendment","depth":8},{"id":93,"text":"while 46 opposed it .","depth":8},{"id":94,"text":"Majority Leader Harry Reid supported it","depth":9},{"id":95,"text":"but only voted 'no ' in the end on procedural grounds","depth":9},{"id":96,"text":"to keep open the possibility","depth":9},{"id":97,"text":"of revisiting it later .","depth":9},{"id":98,"text":"The Senate source says","depth":7},{"id":99,"text":"Manchin 's prime targets","depth":10},{"id":100,"text":"to flip","depth":10},{"id":101,"text":"are all Republicans and similar to those under pressure from outside groups :","depth":9},{"id":102,"text":"Ayotte , Sen. Jeff Flake of Arizona , Sen. Lisa Murkowski of Alaska and Sen. Dean Heller of Nevada .","depth":8},{"id":103,"text":"According to the source ,","depth":9},{"id":104,"text":"proponents hope","depth":10},{"id":105,"text":"that","depth":11},{"id":106,"text":"if Murkowski flips ,","depth":12},{"id":107,"text":"those in favor","depth":15},{"id":108,"text":"of tightening gun laws","depth":15},{"id":109,"text":"will have a good shot","depth":14},{"id":110,"text":"at getting her fellow Alaskan , Sen. Mark Begich , to do the same .","depth":13},{"id":111,"text":"But a source close to Begich , however , told CNN","depth":9},{"id":112,"text":"that it is very unlikely that he 'd change his vote .","depth":9},{"id":113,"text":"He is up for reelection in 2014 in a state","depth":8},{"id":114,"text":"that is very pro-gun .","depth":8},{"id":115,"text":"The NRA is likely to be a power","depth":6},{"id":116,"text":"that looms large over any deal on background checks ,","depth":7},{"id":117,"text":"much like it was during the last debate .","depth":7},{"id":118,"text":"After the compromise background check proposal failed ,","depth":6},{"id":119,"text":"the NRA Institute for Legislative Action released a statement","depth":8},{"id":120,"text":"decrying the `` misguided '' amendment","depth":9},{"id":121,"text":"that ,","depth":11},{"id":122,"text":"it said ,","depth":11},{"id":123,"text":"would `` not reduce violent crime","depth":11},{"id":124,"text":"or keep our kids safe in their schools . ''","depth":11},{"id":125,"text":"`` This amendment would have criminalized certain private transfers of firearms between honest citizens ,","depth":9},{"id":126,"text":"requiring lifelong friends , neighbors and some family members to get federal government permission","depth":10},{"id":127,"text":"to exercise a fundamental right","depth":11},{"id":128,"text":"or face prosecution , ''","depth":11},{"id":129,"text":"the NRA said .","depth":8},{"id":130,"text":"Wayne LaPierre , executive vice president of the NRA , made it clear on Friday","depth":6},{"id":131,"text":"that his organization would not budge on guns .","depth":6},{"id":132,"text":"`` All over this country ,","depth":8},{"id":133,"text":"everywhere","depth":9},{"id":134,"text":"I go ,","depth":9},{"id":135,"text":"people agree ,","depth":7},{"id":136,"text":"they want bad guys taken off the streets","depth":9},{"id":137,"text":"and they want children protected in their schools , ''","depth":9},{"id":138,"text":"he said .","depth":8},{"id":139,"text":"`` And they do n't ' want their freedom taken away . ''","depth":7},{"id":140,"text":"In addition to LaPierre , several potential contenders for the 2016 GOP nomination will take the stage in Houston ,","depth":6},{"id":141,"text":"including Sen. Ted Cruz of Texas , Louisiana Gov . Bobby Jindal , Texas Gov . Rick Perry , former Sen. Rick Santorum of Pennsylvania , and Wisconsin Gov . Scott Walker .","depth":6},{"id":142,"text":"Former vice presidential nominee Sarah Palin spoke to the group as well .","depth":5},{"id":143,"text":"Republican Sen. John McCain of Arizona ,","depth":6},{"id":144,"text":"asked by one of the other victims of the Giffords shooting","depth":7},{"id":145,"text":"if he thought","depth":8},{"id":146,"text":"background checks would come up again ,","depth":8},{"id":147,"text":"said","depth":6},{"id":148,"text":"there was a `` 50-50 '' chance","depth":7},{"id":149,"text":"that it would .","depth":7},{"id":150,"text":"A spokeswoman for Democratic Sen. Max Baucus of Montana , one of the more high-profile Democrats","depth":7},{"id":151,"text":"to vote against the provision ,","depth":7},{"id":152,"text":"told CNN","depth":6},{"id":153,"text":"that","depth":6},{"id":154,"text":"if such a bill were to come up ,","depth":7},{"id":155,"text":"`` Max will evaluate it","depth":8},{"id":156,"text":"based on the feedback","depth":10},{"id":157,"text":"he gathers from the people of Montana ,","depth":10},{"id":158,"text":"just as he always does with any legislation . ''","depth":9},{"id":159,"text":"But she also said","depth":5},{"id":160,"text":"that in his first vote , `` Montanans told Max loud and clear","depth":6},{"id":161,"text":"they did n't support new gun controls in the previous bill . ''","depth":6}],"relations":[{"parent":323,"left":0,"right":322,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":322,"left":300,"right":321,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":300,"left":275,"right":299,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":275,"left":250,"right":274,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":250,"left":215,"right":249,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":215,"left":176,"right":214,"relation":"elaboration","nucl